WEBVTT

1
00:00:11.538 --> 00:00:14.735
Been thinking long...

2
00:00:15.742 --> 00:00:19.007
...as I watched you all along...

3
00:00:21.114 --> 00:00:25.312
...for so long that you knew.
knew yourself...

4
00:00:25.351 --> 00:00:31.551
...that someone
was watching you...

5
00:00:32.458 --> 00:00:37.862
Watching you all the time...

6
00:00:39.799 --> 00:00:43.064
I ask myself...

7
00:00:44.003 --> 00:00:48.235
...what I have to offer.

8
00:00:50.109 --> 00:00:54.380
Why I keep watching you?

9
00:00:54.413 --> 00:00:58.544
Could I be in love with you?

10
00:01:00.000 --> 00:01:06.074
Watch Online Movies and Series for FREE
www.osdb.link/lm

11
00:01:14.167 --> 00:01:15.335
Hey...

12
00:01:15.368 --> 00:01:17.360
...how did you get here?

13
00:01:17.437 --> 00:01:20.429
Namtarn.
can I take a picture with you?

14
00:01:22.442 --> 00:01:25.605
One... two... three...

15
00:01:26.646 --> 00:01:28.773
Thank you.

16
00:01:34.988 --> 00:01:37.081
Want to take a picture?

17
00:02:08.354 --> 00:02:10.456
Can you hold my baton?

18
00:02:10.489 --> 00:02:12.425
Okay. I'm ready.

19
00:02:12.458 --> 00:02:14.620
Big smile. okay?

20
00:02:15.528 --> 00:02:17.864
Your cheeks look like they're
going to burst.

21
00:02:17.897 --> 00:02:21.891
Okay... one... two... three...

22
00:02:36.449 --> 00:02:37.750
Hey. can I ask you something?

23
00:02:37.783 --> 00:02:39.684
Shoot.

24
00:02:42.789 --> 00:02:44.916
How did you die?

25
00:02:51.064 --> 00:02:53.294
I died of old age.

26
00:02:53.399 --> 00:02:56.527
Damn it... I'm serious.

27
00:02:59.572 --> 00:03:02.632
Wait a sec... I have to pee.

28
00:03:11.951 --> 00:03:14.044
Want to know...

29
00:03:14.087 --> 00:03:17.147
...why I got sent
here mid-term?

30
00:03:19.225 --> 00:03:21.427
Hey. it's already 6 PM.

31
00:03:21.460 --> 00:03:23.486
Let's hurry back.

32
00:03:48.588 --> 00:03:50.749
Vichien. wait up!

33
00:03:55.895 --> 00:04:01.162
Chatree Anantpitisuk. come meet
your parents in the dorm.

34
00:04:47.079 --> 00:04:51.015
Pen. follow me downstairs.

35
00:04:54.287 --> 00:04:58.314
Don't worry.
Everyone's asleep.

36
00:06:38.591 --> 00:06:40.650
Where have you been?

37
00:06:41.594 --> 00:06:42.754
What have you been up to?

38
00:06:43.562 --> 00:06:46.766
Why did you do this?
Tell me where you've been!

39
00:06:46.799 --> 00:06:48.034
Don't let me catch
you again!

40
00:06:48.067 --> 00:06:52.061
Did you hear me?
Don't do this ever again!

41
00:06:52.204 --> 00:06:57.141
...though we are apart...

42
00:06:57.176 --> 00:07:04.550
...I can still feel your heart...

43
00:07:04.583 --> 00:07:08.754
...in my embrace.

44
00:07:08.787 --> 00:07:16.889
We once loved each other...

45
00:07:18.064 --> 00:07:19.053
Chatree...

46
00:07:19.098 --> 00:07:21.362
...Miss Pranee asked me to
bring this to you.

47
00:07:28.441 --> 00:07:31.638
Here...
your dad sent this for you.

48
00:07:50.496 --> 00:07:53.624
Hey. where'd you go?
Your dad was here.

49
00:07:59.772 --> 00:08:02.036
Yeah? Well.
where did you disappear to?

50
00:08:06.012 --> 00:08:09.181
You said no one
cares about you.

51
00:08:09.214 --> 00:08:10.282
How about yourself?

52
00:08:10.315 --> 00:08:13.251
Do you care about anyone
else but yourself?

53
00:08:45.584 --> 00:08:48.917
If you've got something good.
you should share it with us.

54
00:08:49.889 --> 00:08:51.957
Why do I have to share it?

55
00:08:51.990 --> 00:08:56.128
Come on...
because we're buddies.

56
00:08:56.161 --> 00:08:59.188
Friends always share
with friends. right?

57
00:09:00.199 --> 00:09:03.293
Let's be friends. okay?

58
00:09:20.152 --> 00:09:23.349
I bet the new boy's a faggot.

59
00:09:23.389 --> 00:09:25.357
Why?

60
00:09:28.427 --> 00:09:30.622
I dunno. He seems like a fairy.

61
00:09:30.729 --> 00:09:34.722
I bet he reads gay porn.

62
00:09:34.800 --> 00:09:36.836
That's why he won't share.

63
00:09:36.869 --> 00:09:39.999
No wonder Miss Pranee
let him off lightly.

64
00:09:40.039 --> 00:09:42.940
And kept the porn
for herself.

65
00:09:42.975 --> 00:09:44.237
Pok.
lend me your sima lotion.

66
00:09:44.276 --> 00:09:47.109
I'm getting a rash again.

67
00:09:51.283 --> 00:09:52.375
Here you go.

68
00:09:53.419 --> 00:09:56.555
Damn! Do you have balls
like a dinosaur?

69
00:09:56.588 --> 00:09:57.783
How come it's all gone?

70
00:09:58.657 --> 00:10:00.682
Nui. do you have any?

71
00:10:02.995 --> 00:10:05.898
No. but I have formalin.
Want some?

72
00:10:05.931 --> 00:10:08.059
Save it for your dad!

73
00:10:13.372 --> 00:10:15.340
Want it?

74
00:10:18.410 --> 00:10:20.435
Err... thanks.

75
00:10:23.582 --> 00:10:24.844
Hold on.

76
00:10:25.784 --> 00:10:27.877
Do you have
any sima lotion?

77
00:10:36.128 --> 00:10:41.361
Pol. Capt. Vichai Chumchong
Sentenced to Prison for Corruption

78
00:10:43.369 --> 00:10:48.807
His Family Pleads for Mercy
from the Judge

79
00:10:58.017 --> 00:11:02.351
Pol. Capt. Vichai Chumchong
sentenced to 25 years in prison...

80
00:11:03.189 --> 00:11:05.521
Chatree. your mom's on the phone.

81
00:11:15.968 --> 00:11:17.833
Mom?

82
00:11:17.870 --> 00:11:19.963
Ton. it's your father.

83
00:11:20.873 --> 00:11:22.067
Umm... Ton...

84
00:11:24.043 --> 00:11:26.170
I asked Pen to move out of
our house. okay?

85
00:11:30.516 --> 00:11:34.543
How come you never pick up
the phone when I call?

86
00:11:46.031 --> 00:11:50.263
If you think that I sent you
away because of Pen...

87
00:11:50.336 --> 00:11:52.395
...then you're wrong.

88
00:11:56.342 --> 00:12:00.802
Umm... how do you like
your new school?

89
00:16:28.614 --> 00:16:32.675
Vichien.

90
00:17:09.288 --> 00:17:12.257
You have to stay
here every night...

91
00:17:13.458 --> 00:17:16.393
...because I'm sleeping
in your bed. right?

92
00:17:38.517 --> 00:17:39.643
Did he faint?

93
00:17:39.685 --> 00:17:43.644
No. I think he sniffed the ether
used to knock out the rabbits.

94
00:17:44.756 --> 00:17:48.783
Don't crowd him. Back off. boys.

95
00:17:49.861 --> 00:17:54.025
Chalemphol. how many times have
I told you not to sniff ether?

96
00:17:54.232 --> 00:17:56.234
He's regaining consciousness.

97
00:17:56.267 --> 00:17:58.395
He's not dead. He's not dead.

98
00:17:59.404 --> 00:18:01.304
It's like I died and
came back to life.

99
00:18:01.340 --> 00:18:03.642
Liar. You were only out
for a few seconds.

100
00:18:03.675 --> 00:18:07.703
But I really felt like I died.

101
00:18:09.681 --> 00:18:11.945
And I had trouble breathing.

102
00:18:11.984 --> 00:18:14.853
And everything was dark.

103
00:18:14.886 --> 00:18:16.081
And I saw...

104
00:18:16.121 --> 00:18:19.147
Wow. I can't believe it!

105
00:18:20.292 --> 00:18:22.317
If anyone wants to know...

106
00:18:23.161 --> 00:18:25.391
...what lies beyond death...

107
00:18:25.430 --> 00:18:27.489
...feel free to consult me.

108
00:18:27.566 --> 00:18:30.636
Hey fatso... no one gives a shit
where your spirit went!

109
00:18:30.669 --> 00:18:32.604
I'm getting hungry.
Let's go.

110
00:19:25.957 --> 00:19:27.822
What the...!

111
00:20:14.873 --> 00:20:17.000
Vichien! Don't jump!

112
00:21:51.736 --> 00:21:53.863
Now you know...

113
00:21:55.073 --> 00:21:58.008
...how I died. right?

114
00:22:03.315 --> 00:22:05.476
Why did you drown yourself?

115
00:22:08.420 --> 00:22:11.412
Who said I drowned myself?

116
00:22:12.724 --> 00:22:15.659
It's more stupid than that.

117
00:22:17.963 --> 00:22:19.931
That day...

118
00:22:20.899 --> 00:22:22.890
...we didn't want
to stop swimming.

119
00:22:24.069 --> 00:22:26.299
It was getting dark.

120
00:22:31.443 --> 00:22:33.411
Help!

121
00:22:33.578 --> 00:22:35.603
Help me!

122
00:22:36.581 --> 00:22:38.811
Hey! Tira is drowning!
Tira is drowning!

123
00:22:51.329 --> 00:22:53.456
Where is he?

124
00:22:55.433 --> 00:22:57.535
Idiots! I fooled you!

125
00:22:57.568 --> 00:23:00.527
You were faking it?
That's pretty funny.

126
00:23:17.289 --> 00:23:18.517
Did you do your
homework yet?

127
00:23:18.556 --> 00:23:21.457
I forgot. It's for the
first period too.

128
00:23:25.597 --> 00:23:26.894
Help me!

129
00:23:27.766 --> 00:23:29.901
Hey... Vichien is drowning.

130
00:23:29.934 --> 00:23:31.960
Help me!

131
00:23:34.205 --> 00:23:37.075
Go ahead and save him.

132
00:23:37.108 --> 00:23:39.134
But he could be faking it.

133
00:23:41.479 --> 00:23:43.606
Help me!

134
00:23:57.929 --> 00:23:59.226
Help me!

135
00:24:15.814 --> 00:24:18.750
Hey. let's go. It's getting late.

136
00:24:18.783 --> 00:24:20.809
Let's go.

137
00:24:23.989 --> 00:24:26.048
Hey. I'm leaving now.

138
00:24:45.944 --> 00:24:49.247
Then how come
they say that...

139
00:24:49.280 --> 00:24:52.375
...Miss Pranee was related
to your death?

140
00:24:56.488 --> 00:24:59.480
Did you read that
newspaper?

141
00:25:06.798 --> 00:25:08.959
It's about my father.

142
00:25:09.034 --> 00:25:12.094
Miss Pranee didn't want
me to find out.

143
00:25:16.374 --> 00:25:18.239
Vichien!

144
00:25:19.210 --> 00:25:20.438
What are you doing?

145
00:25:21.413 --> 00:25:23.515
Who gave you
permission to enter?

146
00:25:23.548 --> 00:25:24.675
Come here.

147
00:25:25.417 --> 00:25:27.681
Why did you do this? Why?

148
00:25:28.720 --> 00:25:30.745
Why? I'll hit you until
I break your hand.

149
00:25:38.196 --> 00:25:41.324
I just wanted to read the
news about my father.

150
00:25:46.304 --> 00:25:49.671
Unfortunately.
Miss Pranee caught me first.

151
00:25:51.576 --> 00:25:54.704
Miss Pranee. Vichien hasn't
returned to the dorm yet.

152
00:26:28.279 --> 00:26:31.339
Before my accident...

153
00:26:32.183 --> 00:26:35.448
...I managed to sneak back in
to steal the newspaper.

154
00:26:43.962 --> 00:26:45.930
Ever since then...

155
00:26:46.898 --> 00:26:51.028
...Miss Pranee has thought
that my death...

156
00:26:51.102 --> 00:26:53.263
...was her fault.

157
00:27:07.886 --> 00:27:10.855
But how come you
have to drown...

158
00:27:10.922 --> 00:27:13.049
...over and over like this?

159
00:27:15.026 --> 00:27:16.994
I don't know.

160
00:27:18.096 --> 00:27:22.226
Will you be stuck like this...
for much longer?

161
00:27:22.333 --> 00:27:24.494
I don't know myself.

162
00:27:25.470 --> 00:27:29.770
But it's really cold
at the bottom.

163
00:28:00.872 --> 00:28:04.069
See... didn't I tell you.

164
00:28:04.108 --> 00:28:08.238
That it must be the boy who
drowned in the pool?

165
00:28:09.380 --> 00:28:13.476
I've seen ghosts
like this before.

166
00:28:15.520 --> 00:28:17.715
At my old house...

167
00:28:17.755 --> 00:28:21.816
a motorcycle crashed rounding
the corner at night.

168
00:28:28.032 --> 00:28:32.093
The driver flew off his bike
and died instantly.

169
00:28:33.304 --> 00:28:35.238
After that night...

170
00:28:35.273 --> 00:28:38.376
...I'd hear the same motorbike...

171
00:28:38.409 --> 00:28:41.675
...skid around the corner
almost every night.

172
00:29:17.115 --> 00:29:21.313
As if the spirit hadn't
been reborn yet...

173
00:29:22.086 --> 00:29:25.317
so it had to re-enact it's death...

174
00:29:25.390 --> 00:29:29.451
...over and over.

175
00:29:47.278 --> 00:29:49.247
What then?

176
00:29:49.280 --> 00:29:51.442
We moved the heck out of there.

177
00:29:51.516 --> 00:29:53.384
No...

178
00:29:53.417 --> 00:29:54.686
How do we help the
spirits get reborn...

179
00:29:54.719 --> 00:29:56.745
...so they stop re-enacting
their own deaths?

180
00:29:57.622 --> 00:30:02.787
Ghosts and humans occupy
separate worlds.

181
00:30:02.860 --> 00:30:06.057
To help a ghost
you must be a ghost.

182
00:30:06.097 --> 00:30:09.167
To be a ghost.
you have to die first.

183
00:30:09.200 --> 00:30:14.332
Unless you can split your spirit
from your body.

184
00:31:21.973 --> 00:31:23.207
Are you crazy?

185
00:31:23.240 --> 00:31:26.233
Why would you want to die?

186
00:31:29.347 --> 00:31:30.541
Ton...

187
00:31:30.581 --> 00:31:33.448
...swear that you won't do it.

188
00:31:39.757 --> 00:31:41.952
Hey. promise me.

189
00:31:45.129 --> 00:31:48.121
Dr. Nui. what the hell
are you looking at?

190
00:31:49.133 --> 00:31:51.436
Something's wrong with Chatree.

191
00:31:51.469 --> 00:31:53.495
He seems strange.

192
00:31:53.571 --> 00:31:56.574
Shit. the other day you said
he wasn't strange.

193
00:31:56.607 --> 00:31:58.633
I know.

194
00:31:58.776 --> 00:32:02.906
But today he seems strange.

195
00:32:02.980 --> 00:32:04.849
Maybe...

196
00:32:04.882 --> 00:32:07.010
...he's going to
jump off the building.

197
00:32:07.852 --> 00:32:11.015
How the hell can he jump
through the grille?

198
00:32:19.397 --> 00:32:21.524
Can you see that water tank?

199
00:32:22.733 --> 00:32:25.725
I've climbed to the top before.

200
00:32:25.803 --> 00:32:27.964
The view is even nicer
than from up there.

201
00:32:31.075 --> 00:32:33.976
I'll take you there some day.

202
00:33:00.171 --> 00:33:03.334
Chatree has disappeared.

203
00:33:14.886 --> 00:33:16.988
Playing during dinner again?

204
00:33:17.021 --> 00:33:20.890
You'll see...
I'll teach you a lesson.

205
00:33:57.595 --> 00:33:59.620
Hey. Chatree! Chatree!

206
00:34:02.767 --> 00:34:03.791
Chatree. are you okay?

207
00:34:03.935 --> 00:34:06.733
Chatree. wake up!

208
00:34:12.043 --> 00:34:13.305
Killed himself. right?

209
00:34:14.278 --> 00:34:16.247
No.

210
00:34:16.280 --> 00:34:18.306
I think he split his spirit
from his body.

211
00:34:18.382 --> 00:34:19.450
What are you talking about?

212
00:34:19.483 --> 00:34:21.384
Splitting spirits from what?

213
00:34:21.452 --> 00:34:22.714
He told me himself...

214
00:34:23.487 --> 00:34:26.684
that he wanted to help his
friend that drowned in the pool.

215
00:34:26.857 --> 00:34:30.850
I suggested he could if he split
his spirit from his body.

216
00:34:42.506 --> 00:34:44.303
Trust me...

217
00:34:44.375 --> 00:34:46.434
...we have to take him
to the old pool.

218
00:34:47.745 --> 00:34:50.680
Miss Pranee.
Chatree killed himself.

219
00:35:26.217 --> 00:35:28.242
Vichien's drowning!

220
00:35:34.592 --> 00:35:36.457
Help me!

221
00:36:11.896 --> 00:36:13.090
Here!

222
00:36:13.130 --> 00:36:14.198
What's that for?

223
00:36:14.231 --> 00:36:17.190
You idiot! To break the lock!

224
00:36:34.885 --> 00:36:37.012
What do we do now?

225
00:36:50.735 --> 00:36:53.871
You told me that no
one cares about you.

226
00:36:53.904 --> 00:36:55.773
How about yourself?

227
00:36:55.806 --> 00:36:57.866
Do you care about anyone
else but yourself?

228
00:37:07.218 --> 00:37:10.244
Hey... let me go!

229
00:37:54.198 --> 00:37:56.167
Are you still mad
at your friends...

230
00:37:56.200 --> 00:37:58.369
...for not saving you from
drowning?

231
00:37:58.402 --> 00:38:00.360
No. I'm not mad anymore.

232
00:38:02.473 --> 00:38:03.641
How about you?

233
00:38:03.674 --> 00:38:05.643
Do you still want to run
away from school?

234
00:38:05.676 --> 00:38:07.668
No. not anymore.

235
00:38:07.711 --> 00:38:11.841
If I did. I would run straight
to Namtarn's embrace.

236
00:38:11.982 --> 00:38:14.883
Hey. hey...
I know what you're thinking.

237
00:38:14.919 --> 00:38:17.114
Don't! I remember the way
you looked at her. too.

238
00:38:17.154 --> 00:38:19.315
I've had my heart set
on her for years.

239
00:38:20.291 --> 00:38:22.486
When will we go visit
her again?

240
00:38:30.868 --> 00:38:32.836
Hey... Ton...

241
00:38:39.977 --> 00:38:42.036
...I've got to leave now.

242
00:39:44.775 --> 00:39:46.675
Hey... Chatree is coming to.

243
00:40:03.394 --> 00:40:05.453
Miss Pranee.
Chatree is fine now.

244
00:40:55.713 --> 00:40:58.876
I never knew our
school was this big.

245
00:40:59.683 --> 00:41:02.914
Hey... Why are you so amazed.
About the side of the school?

246
00:41:02.987 --> 00:41:04.852
I know from experience.

247
00:41:04.888 --> 00:41:07.124
Miss Pranee made me run
around the school before.

248
00:41:07.157 --> 00:41:09.159
Tears are falling from my eyes.

249
00:41:09.192 --> 00:41:12.262
You're the
one who's going to fall.

250
00:41:12.295 --> 00:41:14.465
Okay. calm down.

251
00:41:14.498 --> 00:41:17.366
I was only kidding.

252
00:41:19.403 --> 00:41:20.665
Hey. Ton...

253
00:41:21.572 --> 00:41:24.632
...why didn't you tell Miss Pranee
the truth about Vichien?

254
00:41:24.675 --> 00:41:28.771
Yeah. instead of letting us
all get punished.

255
00:41:31.982 --> 00:41:34.314
I don't think
she'd believe me.

256
00:41:35.285 --> 00:41:39.346
But... we all believe you.

257
00:41:39.490 --> 00:41:43.449
If you happen to
see another ghost...

258
00:41:43.527 --> 00:41:46.519
...feel free to consult me. okay?

259
00:41:46.597 --> 00:41:48.832
But don't consult me.
okay?

260
00:41:48.865 --> 00:41:52.036
Let me be the first one to
consult you then.

261
00:41:52.069 --> 00:41:55.096
Why the heck do you
speak with a lisp?

262
00:42:04.381 --> 00:42:09.512
Chatree Anantpitisuk. please
meet your parents in the dorm.

263
00:42:09.720 --> 00:42:15.659
Chatree Anantpitisuk. please
meet your parents in the dorm.

264
00:42:15.692 --> 00:42:17.956
I guess I'm off.

265
00:42:20.030 --> 00:42:22.089
See you guys next year.

266
00:42:24.334 --> 00:42:26.325
Good luck. man.

267
00:42:26.403 --> 00:42:28.428
Good luck.

268
00:42:41.852 --> 00:42:44.955
Ton. take me to see the
swimming pool. please!

269
00:42:44.988 --> 00:42:47.224
Be patient. Toh.
Let him pack his things first.

270
00:42:47.257 --> 00:42:49.193
Okay.
but then can we see it?

271
00:42:49.226 --> 00:42:50.353
Yes. dear.

272
00:42:55.399 --> 00:42:57.697
Having you been
eating enough food?

273
00:42:57.734 --> 00:43:00.737
You've gotten darker.

274
00:43:00.770 --> 00:43:02.706
And lost weight as well.

275
00:43:02.739 --> 00:43:04.936
You've been playing
outdoors too much. right?

276
00:43:08.045 --> 00:43:10.138
Mom. you're embarassing me.

277
00:43:10.180 --> 00:43:12.045
Why be embarassed?

278
00:43:12.082 --> 00:43:16.246
When you're older I won't
get to hug you anymore.

279
00:43:19.523 --> 00:43:22.549
Toh. stay around here. okay.

280
00:43:22.626 --> 00:43:24.753
Let's get your bags. dear.

281
00:43:46.817 --> 00:43:48.717
Dad...

282
00:43:50.787 --> 00:43:52.880
I like this school now.

283
00:44:26.323 --> 00:44:28.188
Miss Pranee...

284
00:44:35.532 --> 00:44:37.591
Vichien didn't kill himself.

285
00:44:40.938 --> 00:44:46.001
His drowning was
really an accident.

286
00:44:53.483 --> 00:44:56.452
Vichien asked me
to apologize...

287
00:44:57.387 --> 00:45:00.550
...for breaking your
record player that day.

288
00:45:07.998 --> 00:45:09.966
He knows that...

289
00:45:10.968 --> 00:45:13.232
...you were concerned about him.

290
00:45:21.578 --> 00:45:23.546
Thank you. Miss Pranee...

291
00:45:23.580 --> 00:45:25.741
...for always taking care of us.

292
00:45:27.684 --> 00:45:28.776
See you next year.
Miss Pranee.

293
00:46:13.597 --> 00:46:17.829
I still remember the first day
my father took me home.

294
00:46:20.003 --> 00:46:25.100
It was a Friday afternoon
much like any other.

295
00:46:25.175 --> 00:46:29.271
But something had
changed inside of me.

296
00:46:30.414 --> 00:46:33.542
That term. I only grew
two centimetres.

297
00:46:34.351 --> 00:46:36.683
It'll be a while before I'm
a grown man.

298
00:46:39.623 --> 00:46:43.855
Being friends with Vichien made
me see things more clearly.

299
00:47:00.677 --> 00:47:02.770
At that time.
I didn't know...

300
00:47:02.813 --> 00:47:07.682
...what adventures the
next term had in store.

301
00:47:07.851 --> 00:47:11.878
But I knew that I wanted to
rejoin my gang of friends.

302
00:47:11.955 --> 00:47:17.086
Because I've learned that with
one close friend by your side...

303
00:47:17.127 --> 00:47:20.230
...Even the worst things in life...

304
00:47:20.263 --> 00:47:23.461
...will eventually pass...

305
00:47:23.633 --> 00:47:26.568
...in just one short breath.

306
